Nota: 

- For all pending plugins, we need to use new standard dialogs from digikam core instead common dialog from DigikamImagePlugins.  


* New features (Later than 0.9.0 release) :

   - Emboss           : The algorithms must render embossed image in color, not in B&W (like krita).
   - Add Border       : Add capability to preserve original image aspect ratio.
   - Hot Pixels       : Add manual hot pixel selection. Need to implement pixel selection on
                        imageregionwidget from digikam core.
   - Insert Text      : Fix plugin to support multiText edition in a same session (see B.K.O). 
   - Superimpose      : complete rewrite of plugin widget (See B.K.O files #103695 and #103696).

